												<div class="description author withsidebar">
													<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/alexbelth/">Alex Belth</a></h6>
													Alex Belth is the editor of <a href="https://classic.esquire.com/" class="external" target="_blank">Esquire Classic</a> and <a href="http://www.thestacksreader.com/" class="external" target="_blank">The Stacks Reader</a>, a site devoted to preserving great journalism from the pre-digital era.																									</div>
											</div><br class="clear"/><br/>
										</div>

